scripts.name: 60fps bugfix
scripts.description: Literally the best mod ever made. Makes 60fps not only playable, it feels exactly the same as 240fps while *reducing* lag and ping instead of increasing it. Fullscreen recommended. Keywords: starblast.io starblast dueling mod fps bypass unlock uncap if you want more than 60fps, please instead use this mod, it'll solve all your problems.
